The '''Festival of Warriors''' was an [[Standard year/Legends|annual]] [[Gungan/Legends|Gungan]] celebration in which a number of warriors participated, and there was all round frivolity. [[Fassa (Gungan)|Fassa]], the niece of [[Boss/Legends|Boss]] [[Rugor Nass/Legends|Rugor Nass]], was charged with the construction of an arena in [[Lake Umberbool]] on [[Naboo/Legends|Naboo]] to mark the event.

